      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Stella$<BR>There have been many incidents at Lotus Marsh recently, so <FONT color=#a82424>Tamara</FONT> looks like she's having a hard time.<BR>I want to help but…. Things are not going well here either.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-b" mid="210" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="209"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Stella$<BR>We sorceresses are helping out in every possible way. But there's the problem of distance and Kayleen is also tied to the Royal Castle so we lack strength.<BR>If only Karacule was alive to be our moral pillar….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-c" mid="212" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Of course.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-c" mid="213" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(It seems suspicious)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="211"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Stella$<BR>We're trying to help in our own ways, like working together with the Adventurer's Guild to make potions or observing the monsters' behaviours. Things that are harder than you can imagine.<BR>……Really.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-c" image="QN_Npc_SoceressYulliaPrison.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-d" mid="215" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh my, that's bad.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="214"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Stella$<BR>But I heard that at Shadow of Evil Spirits, a sorceress who was sent there lost her way and was trapped there.<BR>She seems to have been captured by the monsters. What a careless child.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Stella heaves a sigh)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n045_soceress_master_stella-accepting-e" mid="217" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Got it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="216"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Stella$<BR>So can you go and save this child?<BR>We can't abandon her. Though our basis is to escape alone….<BR>She should still be safe. Thanks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
